<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	《无能子》的思想及其资料来源（二）
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">二、《无能子》引用</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">儒</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">家及其他思想</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">前面说过，无能子的基本思想是以老庄自然无为的观点来批判儒家的思想。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">因此，他和儒家在</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">主</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">要问题的看法上，可以说是相互对立的。但是，这不能绝对地排斥二者之间相通的地方。事实</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的一些思想，显然受到儒家尤其是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">荀子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">学派的思想影响。如他所说的&ldquo;礼&rdquo;、&ldquo;法&rdquo;、道德的起源及产生过程，实与荀子所说有很多相仿。他说:太古的时候，人与&ldquo;鳞毛羽甲杂处，雌雄扎牡，自然相合，无男女夫妇之别，父子兄弟之序，&rdquo;只是&ldquo;任其自然，遂其天真，无所司牧，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">濛濛</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">淳淳，其理也居且久矣。&rdquo;后来人猿分居，&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">濛</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">淳以散。&rdquo;降及后世，&ldquo;嗜欲愈炽&rdquo;，争夺财富，越来越激烈，仁义道德、礼乐忠信等说教都不起作用了，于是设立刑法监狱和军队来镇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">压</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，这一切皆出于&ldquo;圣人&rdquo;的作为。按荀子说过:&ldquo;礼起于何也?</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">:人</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">生而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有欲，欲而不得，则不能无求</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">求而无度最分界</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">则不能不争。争则乱，乱则穷，先王恶坟乱也，故制礼义以分之，以养人之欲，给人之求，使欲必不穷乎物，物必不屈乎欲。两者相持而长，是礼之所起也。&rdquo;</span><span>20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">且不管他们在论证&ldquo;礼&rdquo;的功用问题上存在着严重分歧，但在思想方法</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，在肯定人类初民之原始</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">濛</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">淳、&ldquo;礼义&rdquo;为后代&ldquo;圣人&rdquo;所作这一点</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，却并无二致。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">又《明本篇》说:&ldquo;无为之为心也，形骸依之以立也，其为常而不殆也。&rdquo;&ldquo;动之则察秋毫之形，审蚊纳之音，静之则不见丘山，不闻</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">雷</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">霆。大之可以包天壤，细之可以</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">入</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">眉睫&hellip;&hellip;明之者，可藏则藏，可行则行，应物立事，旷乎无情。&rdquo;这是说&ldquo;无为&rdquo;是最高境界全在于无心而为，达到这一境界，则动静大小、可藏可行，举措无有不当。按荀子在论述儒家的理想人格</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;圣人&rdquo;的境界时，有过如下一段描述:&ldquo;空石之中有人焉，其名</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">觙</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。其为人也，善射以好思，耳目之欲接，则败其思，蚊虹之声闻，则挫其精。是以避耳目之欲，而远蚊</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">虻</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之声，闲居静心则通。思仁若是，可谓微乎?孟</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">恶败而出妻，可谓能自强矣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有子恶卧而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">焠</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">掌，可谓能自忍矣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">未及好也。避耳目之欲，可谓能自强</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">矣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，未及思也。蚊</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">虻</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之声闻则挫其精，可谓危矣，未可谓微也。夫微者至人，至人也，何强何忍何危?故浊明外景，清明内景，圣人纵其欲、兼其情，而制焉者理矣。夫何强何忍何危?故仁者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之行</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">道也，无为也。圣人之行道也，无强也。&rdquo;</span><span>21</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">荀子认为，象</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">觙</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">、孟子、有子等人的作为，虽然难能可贵，却不能说是最理想的，圣人要&ldquo;无为&rdquo;而&ldquo;无强&rdquo;，却又无往而不适。这种理想的境界，与无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所称道的&ldquo;无为&rdquo;理想，实质</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">又有多少区别?由此可见，世界上没有绝对地互相排斥、互不关联的思想，儒道也是其中的一例。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在有些地方，无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">虽然没有用自己的话公开称赏一些儒家的人物的做法</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">但从其所述的方法与态度看，则显然有赞许的意思。如《孔子说篇》中，讲孔子被困于匡，七日而弦歌不辍，他的学生</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">路对此加以发问。孔</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在回答中说:&ldquo;君子能仁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">人，不能使人仁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我。我能义</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">人，不能使人义</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">我。匡之围，非丘之罪也，丘亦不能使之不围焉。然而可</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">围</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者，丘之形骸也。丘方惚无形</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">冲漠，沦无情</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">杳冥，不知所以忧，故偶谐</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">弦歌尔。&rdquo;言未几，匡人解去。这里虽仍可看出无能子是从&ldquo;无为&rdquo;的立场出发对此加以论述，但较其对儒家所颂扬的&ldquo;圣人&rdquo;的严厉批判态度来说，他在这</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">里</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">对这位儒家学派的创始人实在算是很友好</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">了</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。这是因为，无能子虽对儒家所提倡的礼义忠信持有激烈的观点，但在实质</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，可以看出他所批判的主要是社会</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">那些虚伪的作为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">与</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">其恶劣影响，而并不绝对地排斥个人的德操修养。事实</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，道家虽倡&ldquo;无为&rdquo;却又以&ldquo;无为&rdquo;为一种修养，这在客观</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">使儒道两家在一定条件</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">下</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的合流、相通成为必然。此外，无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">关</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">性命、形骸、生死的议论方面，就多采用玄学和佛学思想。他说:&ldquo;形骸者，性命之器也。犹乎火之在薪，薪非火不焚，火非薪不光。形骸非性命不立，性命借形骸以显，则</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">性</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">命自然冲而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">生</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者也，形骸自然滞</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">死者也。自然生者，虽寂而常生。自然死者，虽摇而常死。&rdquo;</span><span>22</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">又说:&ldquo;夫人大恶者死也，形骸不摇而恨者也。夫形骸血肉耳目不能虚而灵，则非生之具也。故不待不摇而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">偃</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">则</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰死</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，方摇而趋本死矣。所以摇而趋者，凭</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">本不死者耳，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">能自摇而趋者。形骸本死，则非今死，无死矣。死者，人之大恶也。无死可恶，则形骸之外，何足灭否之至和哉?&rdquo;</span><span>23</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">在无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">看来，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">般人所担忧的死，其实只不过是人的形骸的消亡。而形骸本来就是死的，不值得忧虑。其实</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">与</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《列子》中所说多有相合。《列</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">》说:&ldquo;有生之</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">气</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，有形之状，尽幻也。造化之所始，阴阳之所变者，谓之生，谓之死。穷数达变</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">因形移易者，谓之化，谓之幻。造物者，其巧妙，其功深，固难穷难终。固形者，其功显，其功浅，故随起随火。知幻化之不异</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">生</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">死也，始可以学幻。&rdquo;</span><span>24</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">里</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所说的造化之深浅，岂不是无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">所说的&ldquo;性命&rdquo;与&ldquo;形骸</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;吗</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">?&ldquo;性命&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">与</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;形骸&rdquo;，两者本不相同，也终究要各反其本。无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">思想得</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《列</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">》则是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">显</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">然。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;又按《列</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">》一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">书</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，向被视作伪</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">书</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。如高似孙《</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">略》</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">中</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">说:&ldquo;太史公不传列</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，《庄周》未篇列叙诸</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，不及列子。而是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">书写</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《庄子》同者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">十</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">七章，其间尤有浅近迂怪者，故以为出于后于人荟萃而成也</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;明宋</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">濂</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《诸子辨》更明确指出其袭佛学之说多处。如前面所引《列子》思想观点，宋</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">濂</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">以为其&ldquo;有生之气，有形之状，尽幻也&rdquo;一般为袭佛学&ldquo;幻化生</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">灭</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">说</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;万物皆出于机，皆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">入</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">于机&rdquo;为袭佛&ldquo;轮回不息说&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;精神</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">入</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">其门，骨骸反其根&rdquo;为袭佛&ldquo;圆觉四大说。&rdquo;然而学术界一般倾向，认为列子先秦时确有其人并先于庄子，而《列子》一书为后人所伪作。任继愈先生在其主编《中国哲学发展史》(魏晋南北朝卷)中指出《列</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子》乃是玄学颓废派思想的反映，《列子》的思想乃是玄学贵无论向玄学独化论过渡的环节，则《无能子》采用《列子》思想，实质也是对玄学与佛学思想的接纳。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">还</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有《无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">》采用法家思想资料，比较明显的有两个地方:一是在论述历史的进化(按:他认为是退化。)时，一是在论述人性的自私</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">自</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">利之时。无能子说:&ldquo;太古时，裸虫与鳞毛羽甲杂处，&hellip;&hellip;夏巢冬穴，无宫室之制。茹毛饮血，无百谷之食。生自驰，死自仆，无夺害之心，无</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瘞藏</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之事。&hellip;&hellip;无何，裸虫中繁其智虑者，其名</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">人，以法限鳞毛羽甲诸虫。不相播种以食百谷，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是有</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">耒</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">耜</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之用。构土合士以建宫室，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是有斤斧之功</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">设婚嫁以析雌雄</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">牝牡</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是有夫妇之别，父子兄弟之序。为棺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">椁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">衣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">衾</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">以</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瘗</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">藏其死，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是有丧葬之仪。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">结</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">罝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">罘</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">网罗以取鳞毛羽甲诸虫，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">是有刀</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">俎</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之味</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。&rdquo;</span><span>25</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">按这段话，与《韩非子&middot;五蠢篇》所说的历史</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">进化过程基本一致。韩非说:&ldquo;上古之时，人民少而禽兽众，人民不胜禽兽虫蛇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有圣人作，构木为巢以避群害，而民悦之，使王天下，号之</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有巢氏。民食果</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">蓏</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">蚌蛤，腥</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">臊</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">恶臭而伤害腹胃，民多疾病</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">有圣人作，钻隧取火，以化腥</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">臊</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，而民悦之，使王天下，号之</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">曰燧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">人氏。中</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">古</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">之世，天下大水，而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">鲧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">禹决</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">渎</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">。&rdquo;等等。如果我们暂且撇开他们在历史观</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">的分歧，就其对人类初民社会的基本认识来说，则其间的联系也是显然的。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">又《无能子&middot;固本篇》说:&ldquo;棺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">椁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">者，济死甚矣。然其工之心，非乐于济彼也，迫于利也。欲其日售则幸死，幸死非怨于彼也，迫于利也。医者乐病，幸其必</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">瘳</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，非乐于救彼而德彼也，迫于利也。棺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">椁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">与医，皆有济救，幸死幸生之心，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">非有憎爱，各谐其所欲尔。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">故这段话是袭韩非之说。《韩非子&middot;备内篇》说:&ldquo;医善吮人之伤，含人之血，非骨肉之亲也，利所加也。舆人成舆，则欲人之富贵</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">匠人成棺，则欲人之夭死也。非舆人仁而匠人贼也，人不贵则舆不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">售</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">，人不死则棺不买，情非憎人也，利在人之死也。&rdquo;这段话太明显，故不想在此多论了。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
